@startuml seq-keymap-select
'' PlantUML over Mermaid because selecting a keymap set is an ordered handshake: one menu click drives a
'' re-frame event that BOTH installs the set into the live keymap atom AND writes the registry back across
'' the IPC seam to disk. Activation lifetimes + the two fan-out effects matter, so a PlantUML sequence
'' (autonumber + activation + per-concept colour) is the right tool.
!include _vv-theme.iuml

title Settings ▸ Key Bindings ▸ Vim Mode — live install + persist\n[:ui :keymaps] {:active :order :sets}

autonumber "<b>[0]"

actor User #9F8766
participant "menubar\nradio submenu" as UI #2D9574
participant ":keymap/select\n(reg-event-fx)" as RF #4F97D7
collections "app-db\n[:ui :keymaps]" as DB #7590DB
participant ":keymap/install-active\n(fx)" as IA #BC6EC5
database "live keymap atom\n(resolver reads it)" as ATOM #BC6EC5
participant ":keymap/persist\n(fx, debounced)" as PER #B1951D
participant "main config.cljs\nsave! → keybindings.edn" as MAIN #B1951D

User -> UI : click ● Vim Mode
UI -> RF : [:keymap/select "vim"]
activate RF
RF -> DB : registry/select →\n:active ← "vim"
RF -> IA : (fx) install the active set
activate IA
IA -> DB : read active entry\n(builtin? → preset | custom → :extends ⊕ :keymaps)
IA -> ATOM : keymap/install! :vim\n(or install-user! for a custom set)
IA -> RF : dispatch [:input/set-mode (initial-mode)]\n(vim → :normal)
deactivate IA
RF -> PER : (fx) registry/->edn db'
deactivate RF
activate PER
note right of PER
  Debounced ~400 ms: editor edits stream fast,
  so the writes coalesce into a single save.
end note
PER -> MAIN : window.vv.saveKeymap(edn)\n(vv:keymap-save channel)
activate MAIN
MAIN -> MAIN : mkdir + writeFile\n~/.config/vinary-viewer/keybindings.edn
deactivate MAIN
deactivate PER

note over DB, ATOM #FFF6D6
  Two stores stay in sync: [:ui :keymaps] is the persisted source of truth;
  the keymap atom is the live copy the resolver reads on each keydown.
  install-active! is the one-way bridge  db → atom.
end note

legend right
  |= Colour |= Participant / concept |
  |<#9F8766>| User |
  |<#2D9574>| view (radio submenu) |
  |<#4F97D7>| re-frame event (:keymap/select) |
  |<#7590DB>| app-db registry [:ui :keymaps] |
  |<#BC6EC5>| keymap install + live atom |
  |<#B1951D>| IPC seam → main → disk |
endlegend
@enduml
